World Bank Supports Ethiopia 's Educational
ADDIS ABABA , December 23 ( Xinhua ) -- Ethiopian Ministry of Education said here Wednesday that the World Bank and the African Development Bank ( ADB ) have granted over 135 million U.S. Dollars in loan to Ethiopia for the implementation of its five year ( 1997 - 2001 ) educational program .
